How To Build wallet.peercointalk.org
====================================

Dependencies:
1. NodeJS
2. NPM
	
Process
	git clone https://github.com/SigmundAlpha/wallet.peercointalk.org.git
	cd wallet.peercointalk.org
	npm install grunt grunt-combine
	grunt
	
After running the commands, you should find "wallet.peercointalk.org.html"
at the root of the directory.  This is the only file you need to host to
run wallet.peercointalk.org.
